OL,3,CDriver who hit 12-year-old on motorway
OL,4,Cto go on trial
OL,6,FThe driver of a car that hit a 12-year-
OL,7,Fold boy as he was trying to run across
OL,8,Fthe M62 in will go on trial.
OL,10,FCallum Rycroft, 12, died after he was
OL,11,Fhit by a car while attempting to run
OL,12,Facross the motorway at night. He was
OL,13,Ffollowing his father Matthew Rycroft,
OL,14,Fwho and attempted to flee the scene on
OL,15,Ffoot.
OL,17,FShahid Ilyas, who was driving the car
OL,18,Fwhich hit the boy, appeared in court
OL,19,Ftoday and said he "couldn't stop on
OL,20,Fthe motorway".
