OL,4,Cto go on trial
OL,6,FHe has been charged with driving his
OL,7,Fvehicle dangerously on the M62 and
OL,8,FWhitehall Road, .
OL,10,FHe is also accused of failing to stop
OL,11,Fafter a road accident and failing to
OL,12,Freport that accident.
OL,14,FIlyas, 48, of Moorfield Chase,
OL,15,FFarnworth, Bolton, has pleaded not
OL,16,Fguilty to the three charges.
OL,18,FA judge set a trial date of 10 October
OL,19,Fat Bradford Crown Court.
