OL,3,CDriver who hit 12-year-old on motorway
OL,4,Cto go on trial
OL,6,FCallum was hit by a car while
OL,7,Fattempting to cross between junctions
OL,8,F25 and 26 of the M62 at about 9.50pm
OL,9,Fon 5 August 2023.
OL,11,FIn November, Leeds Crown Court heard
OL,12,FCallum's father, Matthew Rycroft, was
OL,13,Fdriving drunk on the motorway when he
OL,14,Fcollided with a barrier and then
OL,15,Foverturned his Audi Q5 on the slip
OL,16,Froad to Hartshead Moor services, near
OL,17,FHuddersfield.
