OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service said
OL,7,FCallum had no speed awareness due to
OL,8,Fhis autism and "should have been under
OL,9,Fthe protection of his father", who
OL,10,Finstead ran across the motorway and
OL,11,Fdid not look back for his son who had
OL,12,Fbeen struck while trying to run with
OL,13,Fhim.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for 10 years last
OL,16,FNovember
